The Quintesson worked hard on Beastbox, realining the parts that had been
thrown around, and mashing all of the dents to the armour with an energon
piston.

Wildrider reached the elevator, and took it up to the third floor, once he
had goten out of the elevator he put Dead-End into a CR chamber. "You'll be
okay Dead-End. Ill be back to check on you buddy". Even though he didnt
show it, he truly did enjoy all of the Stunticons' company, except for
Motormaster, and he would make those Maximals pay for injuring his comerade
in arms. Espeacially Prowl, he kept going over it in his head, the death of
the late Prowl, back on and Autobot shuttle, Scavanger had hit him well
place in the chest, and Prowl's smoking body hit the ground inactive. It
would happen to this Prowl to, Wildrider swore, clenching his fist, as he
headed to the storage room, for more metal for Beastbox.
